      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Implementation Plan\n\nCompleted:\n1. Identified the global script API surface.\n2. Added fragment-scoped selectors for nodes, edges, and groups.\n3. Built script APIs from `activeFragmentId`.\n4. Rejected foreign-fragment reads and mutations.\n5. Kept global storage while exposing only scoped facades to scripts.\n6. Validated the behavior with a dedicated script-scope test graph.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false,
