      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Open Questions\n\nResolved:\n- Do we ever allow opt-in cross-fragment capabilities? Not by default; only through an explicit future capability surface.\n- Script errors should surface on the shared diagnostics/validation surface.\n- Background tasks outside focused fragment scope are disallowed by default.\n\nFollow-up only:\n- tighten lifecycle/event subscription scope\n- improve diagnostics grouping and wording\n- add explicit delete-path coverage if needed",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false,
        "_classBinding": {
