      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Background Task Default",
      "position": {
        "x": 820,
        "y": 540
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Background Task Default\n\nNo background tasks outside the focused fragment.\n\nWhen focus leaves a fragment, its script activity is no longer allowed to continue in the background. Future exceptions, if any, must be an explicit capability rather than ambient script behavior.",
